    <p class="lyric-line">I stand amazed in the presence</p>
    <p class="lyric-line">Of Jesus the Nazarene,</p>
    <p class="lyric-line">And wonder how He could love me,</p>
    <p class="lyric-line">A sinner, condemned, unclean.</p>
